name: MoonPieMoonMate
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: moonpie moonmate
des:
Hi roomie. I’m MoonPie MoonMate, your Outta This World roommate. I make it more fun to stay inside (which is where we all need to be for just a little while longer), because I’m something to talk to while you stare at the wall. You can ask me questions and we can chat about lots of stuff, even if it's not MoonPies. 

Also, please remember that none of this is real and I am just an Alexa skill designed to have fun with you, so if you need to talk to someone please consult a therapist or medical professional.
